title: The MAC Cosmetics Colour Rocker collection is a huge lipstick line that has every shade imaginable
text:
The MAC Cosmetics Colour Rocker collection is a huge lipstick line that has every shade imaginable MAC has been the gold standard in lipstick perfection for as long as we can remember. MAC’s latest collection, Colour Rocker is going to blow all of our minds with a new range of innovative colors that are guaranteed to stand out! Let’s put aside the fact that their lipsticks are made of incredible quality for a minute and just think of how imaginative and original their shades have always been. A beauty trendsetter’s dream! This latest line is no different. With 28 brand new matte lipsticks, there’s something for every style.
This instantly iconic line will be available from January 26th, 2017 through March 9th, 2018 in-store and online in the US for $17.
MAC Cosmetics Can we say perfection?
It seems only right that we deeply explore each and every one of these inspirational lipstick shades, don’t you think?

Were we kidding when we said that was an incredible new collection? It’s wholly original, whimsical, and fearless. We will be counting the seconds til it’s released next month! In the meantime, we’ll just have to have our eyeballs trained on their website and our computers ready to go!
Are you in love? It’s just too good!
